hopobject.body: What sort of music do you listen to? how to test virility Stormy weather reached Croatia on Monday afternoon, raging through Northern and Central parts, as well as the Istrian peninsula, where two Italian yachtsmen were injured. The Croatian capital, Zagreb, was also hit by showers and strong winds which brought down parts of roofs, antennas, traffic signs, tree branches and even snapped some trees in half.
